window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Honey Badger is angry because Honey Badger is hungry. In <i>The Very Hungry Honey Badger</i>, you’ll witness the angriest mammal in the animal kingdom get into several fights as he searches for food.</p> <p>From scaring off buffalo to battling cobras, Honey Badger will show you he does not mess around when his stomach’s grumbling. Someone get him food, pronto!</p> <p>From Kumquat comes the re-telling of a classic story through the voracious appetite of the Honey Badger.</p>"; 
